'''''Virtual Star Embryology''''' is an [[Achievement]] in the category ''[[Meetings in Outrealm: Series V]]''. To complete this achievement, the player needs to defeat the [[Hydro Tulpa]] in [[Co-Op Mode]].

==Trivia==
* This is a reference to one of the [https://ohtori.nu/audiology/albums/02/01_Virtual_Star_Embryology.html insert songs] used in the anime, Revolutionary Girl Utena.
